---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
---
<Layout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Terms of Use for French with Naya tutoring services."
>
  <Navbar />
  <main id="main-content" style="
    background: var(--color-cream);
    padding: 8rem clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) 6rem;
  ">
    <div style="max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p style="
        font-family: var(--font-body);
        font-size: var(--text-label);
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--color-marigold);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      ">Legal</p>
      <h1 style="
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-style: italic;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: var(--text-h1);
        color: var(--color-ink);
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      ">Terms of Use</h1>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-body); color: rgba(26,23,20,0.55); font-size: var(--text-small); margin-bottom: 3rem;">Last updated: May 2025</p>

      <div style="
        font-family: var(--font-body);
        font-size: var(--text-body);
        color: rgba(26,23,20,0.8);
        line-height: 1.75;
      ">
        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--text-h3); color: var(--color-ink); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;">1. Service description</h2>
        <p>French with Naya offers one-to-one online French tutoring sessions for children from Junior Kindergarten through Grade 5 (approximately ages 4–11). All sessions are conducted online via video call. No in-person sessions are offered.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--text-h3); color: var(--color-ink); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;">2. Booking and scheduling</h2>
        <p>Sessions are booked through Cal.com. By booking a session, you agree to provide accurate contact information and to be available at the scheduled time. Booking a session does not guarantee ongoing availability.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--text-h3); color: var(--color-ink); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;">3. Cancellation policy</h2>
        <p>Cancellation terms will be agreed upon between you and Naya at the time of booking. Please provide as much notice as possible if you need to cancel or reschedule a session.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--text-h3); color: var(--color-ink); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;">4. Child safety and parental responsibility</h2>
        <p>A parent or guardian must arrange and consent to tutoring sessions for their child. Parents are responsible for ensuring their child has appropriate access to the required technology (device, internet connection, video conferencing) for sessions.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--text-h3); color: var(--color-ink); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;">5. Use of this website</h2>
        <p>This website is provided for informational purposes and to facilitate bookings. You may not use this website for any unlawful purpose or to transmit harmful, abusive, or spam content through the contact form.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--text-h3); color: var(--color-ink); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;">6. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>French with Naya makes no warranties about the outcomes of tutoring sessions. Results vary by child. We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of this service or website.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--text-h3); color: var(--color-ink); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;">7. Governing law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of Ontario, Canada.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: var(--text-h3); color: var(--color-ink); margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions about these terms, use the contact form on our website.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-chalk);">
        <a href="/frenchwithnaya/" style="
          font-family: var(--font-body);
          font-size: var(--text-small);
          color: rgba(26,23,20,0.55);
          text-decoration: underline;
          text-underline-offset: 3px;
        ">← Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
